{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about/procurement","content_id":"5f55f59f-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"Details of Defence Infrastructure Organisation (DIO) procurement plans and contracts.\r\n","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<h2 id=\"what-we-do\">What we do</h2>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?si=ntCkwzqcJHE3AYSO&amp;v=eXfsr_VtjSM&amp;feature=youtu.be\">What we deliver every day</a> (Youtube video)</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"doing-business-with-dio---entering-the-supply-chain\">Doing business with <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> - entering the supply chain</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/procurement\">Procurement at <abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr></a>: This page outlines the many ways in which you can do business with the Ministry of Defence.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/\">Find a Tender</a>: This central digital platform is where suppliers submit their core business information, which is then shared across multiple bids and customers.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.crowncommercial.gov.uk/information-for-buyers-and-suppliers/start-supplying\">CCS (Crown Commercial Services) Frameworks</a>: Search for existing suppliers on relevant frameworks and lots. To become a supplier through CCS you have to respond to a contract notice and succeed in the tender process. Details of how to register your interest in a tender are contained in the contract notice.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://forms.office.com/pages/responsepage.aspx?id=7WB3vlNZS0iuldChbfoJ5QZ1XaOZ5HBDguEU0NG4CFdURDJFTjZMRVZSUlFQU0xMOUlTSlQ3RUgxSy4u\"><abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> Opt in for Updates and Events</a>: By completing this short opt in form you will be added to the mailing list to receive <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> and event notifications.</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"follow-us\">Follow us</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Read the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://insidedio.blog.gov.uk/\">Inside <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> blog</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Watch our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@DIO_MOD\">YouTube videos</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Follow us on Twitter at <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.twitter.com/mod_dio\">mod_DIO</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Deleted section about a webinar which has now taken place.","public_timestamp":"2025-12-12T09:52:46Z"},{"note":"Updated information.","public_timestamp":"2025-10-28T13:24:11Z"},{"note":"Added information on  'DIO Procurement Webinar – 2 December 2025'","public_timestamp":"2025-10-21T16:00:04Z"},{"note":"Added information on the Construction Professional Services 2 online webinar.","public_timestamp":"2025-04-29T13:40:06Z"},{"note":"Added information on the 'Defence Procurement Research Technology Exportability (DPRTE) 2025 event'.","public_timestamp":"2025-03-13T15:29:53Z"},{"note":"Added information on two upcoming procurement reform webinars.","public_timestamp":"2025-01-08T15:26:07Z"},{"note":"Added information about the DIO Procurement Pipeline Webinar, Wednesday 27 November.","public_timestamp":"2024-10-08T09:19:29Z"},{"note":"Updated 'Dates for your diary' announcement on the Procurement Pipeline webinar.","public_timestamp":"2024-06-03T08:39:34Z"},{"note":"Added information on attending DIO's Procurement Pipeline webinar.","public_timestamp":"2024-04-17T13:26:29Z"},{"note":"Added a link to 'The Official Transforming Public Procurement Knowledge Drops'.","public_timestamp":"2024-02-27T12:15:26Z"},{"note":"Added information on upcoming events and procurement reform.","public_timestamp":"2023-12-15T14:50:59Z"},{"note":"Updated information on Defence Infrastructure Organisation (DIO) procurement plans.","public_timestamp":"2023-11-23T10:26:12Z"},{"note":"Updated 'DIO procurement pipeline' section.","public_timestamp":"2023-10-13T09:35:55Z"},{"note":"Updated information on doing business with DIO. ","public_timestamp":"2023-09-15T13:18:12Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2018-03-28T14:22:53Z"},{"note":"Added information about the Commercial Strategy.","public_timestamp":"2018-03-28T14:22:53Z"}],"headers":[{"id":"what-we-do","level":2,"text":"What we do"},{"id":"doing-business-with-dio---entering-the-supply-chain","level":2,"text":"Doing business with DIO - entering the supply chain"},{"id":"follow-us","level":2,"text":"Follow us"}],"organisation":"73068a99-7122-4cad-a876-35ca0b0778b4","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"procurement","first_published_at":"2014-01-06T12:29:50+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about/procurement","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about/procurement","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about/procurement","content_id":"5f55f59f-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"procurement","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-12-12T09:52:46Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Procurement at DIO","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation/about/procurement","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT496","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation","content_id":"73068a99-7122-4cad-a876-35